  "title": "Mechanical Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Apply specialized knowledge to implement and maintain pharmaceutical or biological processes</li><li>Calculate, organize, and document data for standard process flow sheets, including instrumentation and control aspects</li><li>Assist in process and unit operation modelling</li><li>Operate processing equipment following correct sequences, specifications, and instructions</li><li>Conduct basic tests and measurements during production to monitor variables such as temperature, density, pressure, and viscosity</li><li>Perform maintenance, troubleshoot, and resolve standard engineering issues in existing processes or equipment</li><li>Adhere to established processes and procedures to ensure regulatory compliance</li></ul><p></p>",
